295
00:19:11,316 --> 00:19:13,011
...and l still have to make muffins.

296
00:19:13,185 --> 00:19:14,812
Well, don't make them.

297
00:19:14,987 --> 00:19:16,147
But it's the holidays...

298
00:19:16,321 --> 00:19:19,313
