and some of our colleagues came by...

434
00:27:21,039 --> 00:27:23,769
<i>...for a little celebration</i>
<i>for the end of the semester.</i>

435
00:27:23,942 --> 00:27:25,534
Hi, Joy.

436
00:27:25,710 --> 00:27:28,611
<i>Did you at least take care</i>
<i>of the list that l gave you?</i>

437
00:27:30,081 --> 00:27:32,811
Oh, Stephen, how do you expect me
to get everything done...

438
00:27:32,984 --> 00:27:34,918
...especially with your party
coming up?

439
00:27:35,086 --> 00:27:37,611
Look, l'll do it tomorrow, hon.
Seriously, l promise.

440
00:27:37,789 --> 00:27:39,689
Tomorrow is gonna be....

441
00:27:39,858 --> 00:27:41,519
Stephen, you've gotta hear this.

442
00:27:41,693 --> 00:27:44,526
Honey, l'll be home as soon as l can.
l love you.

443
00:27:46,131 --> 00:27:47,894
l love you too.

444
00:28:23,301 --> 00:28:24,893
Joy?

445
00:28:27,238 --> 00:28:30,537
-Joy.
-Yeah, l'm down here.

446
00:28:30,709 --> 00:28:32,506
Oh, what happened?
Are you all right?

447
00:28:32,677 --> 00:28:33,701
Oh, yeah.

448
00:28:33,878 --> 00:28:34,902
Oh, Lordy.

449
00:28:35,447 --> 00:28:38,541
l just fell off the ladder.

450
00:28:39,884 --> 00:28:41,351
This is dangerous.

451
00:28:42,353 --> 00:28:44,753
l'm just trying
to get the decorations up.

452
00:28:44,923 --> 00:28:47,721
You know how l like
to be the first on the block...

453
00:28:47,892 --> 00:28:50,918
...with their lights up? l'm last.

454
00:28:51,096 --> 00:28:54,759
l have told you, you shouldn't
be doing this stuff by yourself.

455
00:28:55,734 --> 00:28:57,599
Yeah.

456
00:28:57,769 --> 00:29:01,330
You're right. This is ridiculous.

457
00:29:01,840 --> 00:29:03,501
What am l doing?

458
00:29:06,044 --> 00:29:07,170
Do you have any paint?

459
00:29:08,313 --> 00:29:11,578
Paint? Yeah, l think so. Why?

460
00:29:16,855 --> 00:29:21,258
<i>And in local ClF playoff action:</i>
<i>Boom! Down he goes.</i>

461
00:29:21,426 --> 00:29:25,487
-That was a freaking awesome hit.
-That guy got trucked.

462
00:29:25,663 --> 00:29:29,099
